{
  "page": "Did you know/62",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that the first seat from where <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a> ruled was called the <a href=\"/index.php/Aegonfort\" title=\"Aegonfort\">Aegonfort</a>? Aegon eventually decided it was not suited to be the seat of power for a king, so he temporarily moved his family from <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> back to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>. The Aegonfort was razed to the ground and construction of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> began.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/62&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings&#58; Aegon I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403182454\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 95/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8552/1000000\nPost‐expand include s